description:
*All Are Welcome in the Church, Even LGBTQ+* | Michael Carducci and Kezia Chisholm join us for a great discussion on the church's approach to sexuality. Jesus says "Come unto Me...", addressing ALL people, yet over the years, the Church has differed from that invitation, leaving the false idea that those trapped in sexual sin are too far from God's reach. Michael shares stories and his personal experience of how an act of kindness and following Christ's method speaks louder than any verbal argument against the LGBTQI+ lifestyle. @comingoutministries3159
